        }
      ],
      "section_title": null,
      "unit_id": "2",
      "text": "Many studies have validated the concept of using DNA vaccines for both protection and therapy against these protozoan parasites in a variety of mouse models. The challenge now is to translate what has been achieved in these models into veterinary or human vaccines of comparable efficacy."
    },
